text: Prem Nagar railway station (Urdu and ) is located in Prem Nagar village, Kasur district of Punjab province of the Pakistan. The railway station also serves the Lahore Dry Port, located adjacent to the station. ==See also== * List of railway stations in Pakistan * Pakistan Railways ==References== ==External links== * Official Web Site of Pakistan Railways Category:Railway stations in Kasur District Category:Railway stations on Karachi–Peshawar Line (ML 1)
